Company : CODETECH IT SOLUTIONS                                                                                                                                                                                   Domain : Java Programming 
ID : CT6WDS2394
Duration : November 2024 to January 2025

Overview of the Task : 

The task is to create a basic calculator program in Java. The program should allow the user to:

Input two numbers.
Select a mathematical operation (addition, subtraction, multiplication, division).
Perform the operation based on user input.
Display the result to the user.
Requirements
The program should ask the user to input two numbers.
The program should prompt the user to choose one of the following operations:
Addition (+)
Subtraction (-)
Multiplication (*)
Division (/)
The program should perform the chosen operation and display the result.
If the user chooses division, the program should handle the possibility of division by zero.
